function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorSign)

	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(s_Moireach_Follower)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONV_MOIREACH_BEAR_GIZMO, idActorPlayer, idFollower)
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	-- Adding another setter here so debug phase jumping works
	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(s_Moireach_Follower)
	
	-- Move to conversation position
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idFollower)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idFollower, ID_MARKER_STAGE_LOCATION, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idFollower, ID_MARKER_STAGE_LOCATION)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idFollower)
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("QST_Scos_Confrontation", idSelf, idSelf)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idFollower, 0.5)
	
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	-- Fake stage Moireach to outside of camp
	idClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(NPC_MOIREACH_QUEST_01)
	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONV_MOIREACH_03, idActorPlayer, idClone)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idClone, CONV_MOIREACH_03)
	
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, ID_MARKER_CAMP_MOVETO, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idClone, 1.0)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	-- Fake stage Moireach to outside of camp
	idClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(NPC_MOIREACH_END)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, ID_MARKER_QUESTEND, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idClone, 1.0)	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	idClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(id_Moireach_Bear)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idClone) then
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idSelf, "QST_Scos_TendingNature_CloneSuppress")
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, marker_Bear_RunTo, "npc_run", false)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idClone, 0.5)
	end
end
